      %h3.text-center What is Rust?
      %p Rust is a systems programming language from Mozilla built with safety, concurrency, and performance in mind. Its novel approach to memory safety and its rich type system make it an excellent choice for writing fast, secure, and reliable programs. Learn more at <a href="https://www.rust-lang.org/">The Rust Programming Language</a>.

