      %h3.text-center What is Ruma?
      %p Ruma is a collection of Matrix applications and libraries written in Rust. Ruma's approach to Matrix emphasizes correctness, security, stability, and scalability. Read and download Ruma source code on <a href="https://github.com/ruma">GitHub</a>. Get caught up with the latest developments in the <a href="/news/">news</a> and on <a href="https://twitter.com/ruma_io">Twitter</a>. Join the discussion in <a href="https://matrix.to/#/#ruma:matrix.org">#ruma:matrix.org</a>.
